# Large and binary files
# NOTE:
#   It is generally considered bad practice to version control binary asset
#   files in the same repo as text code, but you can attempt to proceed anyway
#   by commenting out these lines.
*.hqx
*.bin
*.exe
*.dll
*.deb
*.dmg
*.iso
*.img
*.msi
*.msp
*.msm
*.mid
*.midi
*.kar
*.mp3
*.ogg
*.m4a
*.ra
*.3gpp
*.3gp
*.mp4
*.mpeg
*.mpg
*.mov
